urnai Cathedral (1171) Image:Hama-AlNouri minaret.jpg|Nur Al-Din Mosque, Hama (1172) <!-- Image with inadequate rationale removed: Image:Ikorta church.JPG|Ikorta church (1172) --> Image:Verona Italy San Zeno DSC08194.JPG|San Zeno Bell Tower, Verona (1173) Image:Maria Lach 02.jpg|Maria Laach Abbey (1177) </gallery>
